---
import MapImage from "/public/billeder/maps.png";
import PinIcon from "/public/billeder/pin.png";
---

<section class="community">
  <h2 class="mobile-heading">Find dit tøjfællesskab</h2>

  <div class="content">
    <div class="map-wrapper">
      <img src={MapImage.src} alt="Kort over Danmark med eventsteder" class="map" />

      <a href="/Roskilde" class="marker" style="top: 60%; left: 77.5%;">
        <img src={PinIcon.src} alt="Marker" class="marker-default" />
        <img src="/billeder/PinHover-Roskilde.png" alt="Hover Marker" class="marker-hover" loading="lazy"/>
      </a>
      <!-- <a href="/" class="marker" style="top: 60%; left: 85%;">
        <img src={PinIcon.src} alt="Marker" class="marker-default" />
        <img src="/billeder/PinHover-AAU.png" alt="Hover Marker" class="marker-hover" />
      </a> -->
      <a href="/Ringkøbing" class="marker" style="top: 46%; left: 18%;">
        <img src={PinIcon.src} alt="Marker" class="marker-default" />
        <img src="/billeder/PinHover-Ringkobing.png" alt="Hover Marker" class="marker-hover" loading="lazy" />
      </a>
      <a href="/Ribe" class="marker" style="top: 69%; left: 25%;">
        <img src={PinIcon.src} alt="Marker" class="marker-default" />
        <img src="/billeder/PinHover-Ribe.png" alt="Hover Marker" class="marker-hover" loading="lazy" />
      </a>
      <a href="/Nørrebro" class="marker" style="top: 59%; left: 83%;">
        <img src={PinIcon.src} alt="Marker" class="marker-default" />
        <img src="/billeder/PinHover-Norrebro.png" alt="Hover Marker" class="marker-hover" loading="lazy" />
      </a>
      <a href="Lyngby/" class="marker" style="top: 57%; left: 85%;">
        <img src={PinIcon.src} alt="Marker" class="marker-default" />
        <img src="/billeder/PinHover-Lyngby.png" alt="Hover Marker" class="marker-hover" loading="lazy" />
      </a>
      <a href="/Fredericia" class="marker" style="top: 62%; left: 40%;">
        <img src={PinIcon.src} alt="Marker" class="marker-default" />
        <img src="/billeder/PinHover-Fredericia.png" alt="Hover Marker" class="marker-hover" loading="lazy" />
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="text">
      <h2 class="desktop-heading">Find dit tøjfællesskab</h2>
      <p>Vælg fra listen herunder hvilket tøjfællesskab du vil være en del af, og kom til månedlige bytte-saloner i dit nærområde.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* ─── MOBILE-FIRST BASE STYLES ─── */
  .community {
    background-color: #fefde9;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 4vw, 2rem);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-family: "Oregon LDO DemiBold", sans-serif;
  }

  .mobile-heading {
    display: block;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .desktop-heading {
    display: none;
  }

  .content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 3rem;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .map-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .map {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .marker {
    position: absolute;
    transform: translate(-50%, -100%);
    width: 5vw;
    max-width: 40px;
    cursor: pointer;
    z-index: 1;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .marker-default,
  .marker-hover {
    position: absolute;
    width: 100%;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  .marker-hover {
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 2;
    min-width: 8rem;
  }

  .marker:hover {
    z-index: 10;
  }

  .marker:hover .marker-default {
    opacity: 0;
  }

  .marker:hover .marker-hover {
    opacity: 1;
    pointer-events: auto;
    width: 60px;
  }

  .text {
    font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 2vw, 1.2rem);
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 500px;
    text-align: center;
    align-self: center;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  /* ─── DESKTOP LAYOUT (from 768px up) ─── */
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .content {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 4rem;
      width: 80vw; /* max 80% of viewport */
      max-width: 80vw;
      margin: 0 auto;
      align-items: start;
      margin-top: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .map-wrapper {
      margin: 0;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .text {
      text-align: left;
      font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.5vw, 1.4rem);
      max-width: none;
    }

    .mobile-heading {
      display: none;
    }

    .desktop-heading {
      display: block;
      text-align: left;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.4rem);
    }

    .marker {
      width: 4vw;
      max-width: 30px;
    }

    .marker:hover .marker-hover {
      width: 80px;
    }
  }
</style>
